{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>未料2015年爆出涉嫌前往海外賣淫，收取約韓幣3500萬元（約18.5萬港元），遭起訴後也就此消失於當地歌壇。未料這陣子傳出G.NA已經結婚生子，周遭人士也回應相關傳聞。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20240930/917464244646055936406915.jpeg/ZNjujodOruCMgavBWtpOiJQWkvuE5NJDQ_GDlUPxg5U\" alt=\"G.NA（IG@missginachoi87）\"><figcaption>G.NA（IG@missginachoi87）</figcaption></figure><p>點擊查看更多G.NA的相片：</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126196187435634688183065.jpeg/r-oYjtraYvyEeibWr36sGY4qSI1Kj5_uIejDIiHowyI\" alt=\"G.NA（IG@baidugnabar）\"><figcaption>G.NA（IG@baidugnabar）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126196189646163968940712.jpeg/Ec26Q9yioC1ZmvHWnjkI5d5WmE_2sVXMoM7MHKDOzBw\" alt=\"G.NA（IG@baidugnabar）\"><figcaption>G.NA（IG@baidugnabar）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126196192729108480320794.jpeg/-5OD0vmMOktGWpZDPWSSoR3k6te7zIILOvz4bDr8-Gw\" alt=\"G.NA（IG@baidugnabar）\"><figcaption>G.NA（IG@baidugnabar）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126196194662813696423876.jpeg/kjY0TmULz0wY3wYpL922sLt02KemQb3P5vRtpOb0baQ\" alt=\"G.NA（IG@baidugnabar）\"><figcaption>G.NA（IG@baidugnabar）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126196197112418304382175.jpeg/PMMkm7kGqw7f18FExaaUp8yUXGhbmNxoztjHqc7Yx6k\" alt=\"G.NA（IG@baidugnabar）\"><figcaption>G.NA（IG@baidugnabar）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126196186873597952135274.jpeg/HK9Dlftf4DAwvkVOCCRr_S9b_KUGaNkRIQTBfCEEwXw\" alt=\"G.NA（IG@baidugnabar）\"><figcaption>G.NA（IG@baidugnabar）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126196188983463936417208.jpeg/9gfjq9eIGgqVxbi7t_AHpCPpyfUkBrtnjaTup42k7qc\" alt=\"G.NA（IG@baidugnabar）\"><figcaption>G.NA（IG@baidugnabar）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"htt